posting_body: ['Welcome to Larson at University Place!', 'Experience the best that University Place and the South Sound have to offer.', 'Boasting a variety of floor plans ranging from thoughtfully designed Studios to amazing Two-Bedrooms, all featuring indulgent finishes and high-end appliances.', 'Larson residents are able to perfectly balance work and play with planned amenities like a private fitness studio and reservable office space in addition to our roof-top retreat and pet spa; there is something for everyone!', "Minutes from all your favorite shopping and abundant recreational opportunities, you have a can't miss combination of style and convenience at Larson!", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 84', 'OR Text', '84', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1220 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Washer/Dryer -', 'In Unit', '- Dishwasher', '- Microwave', '- Breakfast Nook', '- Walk-In Closets', '- Heating', '- Cable Ready', '- Double Pane Windows', '- Granite Countertops', '- Smoke Free', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Disposal', 'Community Amenities', '- Pet Spa', '- 24 Hour Availability', '- Pet Play Area', '- Elevator', '- Package Service', '- Grills', '- Conference Room', '- Fitness Center', '- Business Center', '- Clubhouse', '- Key Fob Entry', '- Public Transportation', '- Bike Storage', '- Renters Insurance Program', '- Lounge', '- Controlled Access', '- Recycling', 'Pet Policy', 'Dogs and cats allowed.', 'Pet Limit- 2 Weight limit-', '70 lbs', 'One time Fee- $600 2nd Pet-', 'additional $300 fee', 'Monthly pet rent- $45 per pet', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 8:30AM-5:30PM', 'Larson Apartments', '3706 Larson Lane W, University Place, WA, 98466', 'dB8x0wafergj']
